						               													<description>Your story - your rules!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Zombies wherever you look. Nobody knows Where they come from and what they want. Mindless, hungry and unstoppable, they hunt the living. Zombies! All that's left is to arm yourself to the teeth just to see another day. You are part of a group of survivors, trying to fight against overpowering Undead. All for one, or maybe sacrifice one for all? Where do the Zombies come from, and how can you get rid of them? Maybe they are part of a bigger plan? Make your own story and see for yourself what happens.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Zombia is a narrative card game in the Mini Story series by Noris Spiele. Cards determine their role, their relations to each other and their secret goals. A game last over five rounds, after which the winner(s) are identified as related to their goals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
